A scrap-book with misc notes about things that weren't obvious at first sight.
Intended for SMD developers, not intended to replaces RCP tutorials. 

= i18N = 

To localize plugin declarations (plugin.xml):
/smd-rcp/plugin.properties
	menu.help.label = Help
	menu.help.mnemonic = H
/smd-rcp/plugin.xml
	label="%menu.help.label"
    mnemonic="%menu.help.mnemonic">
/smd-rcp/META-INF/MANIFEST.MF
	Bundle-Localization: plugin

